The first of MANY Colombia dumps to come… hope you’re ready! @bahiaconchatayrona was an incredible start to the most magical vacation!

And this is just the beginning…
Let’s swing & splash all day

Anyone else love the outdoors? 🌳🍃🌲🌱@bosko_guatape does the most incredible job of creating a seamless & unique living experience to make you feel like the #colombian jungle is home. Bright lights and contact with others is minimal, bathrooms are outdoors, breakfast is flavorful, views are amazing and life just feels a bit more relaxed up here… especially after a couple massages and a late night jacuzzi session 💦
